1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 15=

17
00:01:18,720 --> 00:01:19,600
Li Yunhe,

18
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:20,320
weren't you arrested

19
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:21,680
on suspicion of murder?

20
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,080
Well, Mrs. Zhou,

21
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,720
the whole thing was a misunderstanding.

22
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:25,760
However,

23
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,520
with my own wit

24
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,960
and intelligence,

25
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:30,120
I managed to clear up
this misunderstanding.

26
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:31,400
Please rest assured.

27
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,240
And if I may ask, Mrs. Zhou,

28
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,400
just now,

29
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,800
the Marquis's heir

30
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,040
came to the Zhou Manor.

31
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:38,920
What is his purpose?

32
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,520
You still have the nerve to ask me that?

33
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,560
You'd barely been
a live-in son-in-law for a few days,

34
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,160
and on your wedding night,
you slept in a brothel.

35
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,400
Right after that, you kept making eyes

36
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,520
at a servant girl.

37
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,960
Have you no sense of decency?

38
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,640
Speaking of that servant girl...

39
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,600
That's precisely why

40
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,840
I've come here today.

41
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,400
What

42
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,880
do you mean?

43
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,040
I believe

44
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,720
you've already heard

45
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,320
of my recent exploits outside the manor.

46
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,640
Although I've been discarded
by the Zhou family,

47
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:05,800
I still wish

48
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,640
to part with your family on good terms.

49
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:09,280
I hope you can grant me this, Mrs. Zhou.

50
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:11,280
I have indeed

51
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,880
heard of your affairs.

52
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,080
You won the verse match

53
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,040
against the Marquis's heir,

54
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,240
advised the Prefect
on stabilizing grain prices,

55
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,240
and at the Chunfeng Pavilion
poetry gathering,

56
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,720
you outshone the new Top Scholar,

57
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:22,120
and that mess got you
briefly wanted by the authorities.

58
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,240
Given your current reputation
in Feng City,

59
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,840
being a live-in son-in-law for my family

60
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,280
is more than good enough.

61
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,000
However,

62
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,520
are you truly willing
to stake your bright future

63
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,080
on buying the freedom of a servant girl?

64
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,520
My word is my bond.

65
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,280
I stand by what I say.

66
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,160
No second thoughts.

67
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:37,880
Alright.

68
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,960
A man of true sentiment, I see.

69
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:40,880
Very well.

70
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,440
Since your marriage contract
with my family

71
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,360
has already been dissolved,

72
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,520
and you want a mere servant girl,

73
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,760
I grant this request.

74
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,840
Thank you, Mrs. Zhou,
for your generosity.

75
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:49,960
Now,

76
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,040
would you please

77
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,760
call Yu out here?

78
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,760
Yu?

79
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,160
Are you certain

80
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,880
there's a servant
named Yu in the Zhou Manor?

81
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,800
Mrs. Zhou,

82
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:00,040
this joke of yours

83
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,840
is not the least bit funny.

84
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:02,920
Attendants!

85
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,360
Summon all the hired hands

86
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,160
and maidservants of the manor.

87
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:19,520
No more?

88
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,360
They're all here.

89
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,280
That can't be right.

90
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,520
Where is Yu?

91
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,520
I don't know her.

92
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,640
Have you seen Yu?

93
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,240
No.

94
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,280
Never heard of her.

95
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,920
How is that possible?

96
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,640
Where has my Yu gone?

97
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,480
Mrs. Zhou,

98
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,040
the person I'm looking for is

99
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:42,440
that servant girl who grew up
in the Zhou Manor,

100
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,880
the one who also knows
how to make Gambiered Silk,

101
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,760
that beautiful girl, Yu.

102
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:46,840
I'm certain of it.

103
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:49,520
There's no servant
named Yu in the Zhou Manor.

104
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,760
If you don't want to give me Yu,

105
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,120
just say so outright.

106
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,480
No need to toy with me like this.

107
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:55,680
Li Yunhe,

108
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:57,040
I have shown you every woman

109
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:57,680
in the Zhou Manor.

110
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,040
What more do you want from me?

111
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:01,320
If you won't hand Yu over

112
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,440
to me,

113
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,920
even if I have to
turn this entire manor upside down,

114
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,280
I will find her!

115
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,320
How dare you!

116
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,680
What do you take the Zhou Manor for?

117
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:09,680
Guards!

118
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,720
Throw this scoundrel out!

119
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,320
Mrs. Zhou, listen to me.

120
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,760
Yu has to be in the Zhou Manor.

121
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:16,840
Just give her to me,

122
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:17,840
and I'll never trouble you.

123
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:19,640
You just don't know when to quit.

124
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:23,960
(Zhou Manor)

125
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:24,520
(Zhou Manor)
Let go of me!

126
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:25,880
Let me go!

127
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,240
Get lost!

128
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,720
Hey!

129
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,640
Open the gate!

130
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,240
Mrs. Zhou!

131
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:33,880
My lady.

132
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,840
Give Yu back to me!

133
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,160
Listen,

134
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,640
I'm about to hit it big.

135
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,560
If you don't give me Yu back,

136
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,640
I'll be the sworn enemy
of the Zhou family!

137
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,720
Yu.

138
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,920
Stop this, Li Yunhe.

139
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:55,360
The Zhou family
has already discarded you.

140
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,040
I know that.

141
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,640
Mr. Li,

142
00:04:58,640 --> 00:05:00,160
what my lady means is,

143
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,120
please leave the Zhou Manor
right this instant,

144
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,560
or we'll call the constables.

145
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,360
Your lady?

146
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,920
Yu,

147
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:23,760
don't tell me

148
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,480
you're actually the Zhou heiress?

149
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,560
Yu! I...

150
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,400
Mr. Li.

151
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,040
Yu!

152
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,680
Mrs. Zhou has already
betrothed Miss Zhou

153
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,960
to the Marquis's heir.

154
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,640
Please go back.

155
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,240
The Marquis's heir?

156
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,560
The die is cast.

157
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,640
There's nothing left

158
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,080
between my lady and you.

159
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,040
Just leave right away.

160
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,440
You ancient people

161
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,320
are all liars.

162
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:08,640
(Zhou Manor)

163
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:42,700
My lady, Mr. Li has left.

164
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,440
He's gone?

165
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,840
It's better this way.

166
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,880
Saves us from endless entanglements

167
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,760
and constant worry.

168
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,200
I don't get it.

169
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,960
You clearly care so much for Mr. Li.

170
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:56,320
Why make him leave?

171
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,440
Haven't you seen it yet?

172
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,200
Li Yunhe

173
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,760
absolutely detests the title of

174
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:02,720
the Zhou live-in son-in-law.

175
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:03,960
The very first thing he did

176
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,000
after gaining some power

177
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:07,120
was to hurry and leave the Zhou family.

178
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:08,960
But wasn't that because

179
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,600
he mistook Miss Song for you,

180
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,520
my lady?

181
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:12,600
It's not as simple

182
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,600
as you think.

183
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,560
You saw what Li Yunhe was like

184
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,680
when he first arrived.

185
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,640
But the moment
he signed that divorce letter,

186
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:19,920
it was as if

187
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,160
he became a completely different person,

188
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,080
full of spirit,

189
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,480
brimming with talent.

190
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,960
Do you think this is normal?

191
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,240
But my lady,

192
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:30,040
no matter what Mr. Li becomes,

193
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:32,480
with your looks,
your family background, your character,

194
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,760
you're more than good enough for him.

195
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,160
You don't understand.

196
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,760
(Yu,)

197
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,480
(go sit back down)

198
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,760
(in a moment)

199
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,520
(and keep a bit of distance from me)

200
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:42,840
(because I'm about)

201
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:43,800
(to unleash)

202
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,880
(some serious swagger.)

203
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,240
Both of us, stranded
at the ends of the earth,

204
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,640
why must we have known
each other before?

205
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,640
(Fear not the lonely road ahead.)

206
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:08,040
(The whole world will know your name.)

207
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:11,920
(Nothing in this world
has ever been perfect.)

208
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,720
I only wish that we may live long

209
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,360
and share this moonlight
across a thousand miles.

210
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,920
Chunxiang,

211
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,160
do you understand the greatness

212
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:21,160
of the poetry
that comes from Li Yunhe's mouth?

213
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,880
I can barely read a few words.

214
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,840
Behold

215
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:28,480
the Yellow River,
descending from heaven,

216
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:31,040
surging to the sea, never back.

217
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,640
Li Yunhe's talent

218
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:36,840
is like that very river,
pouring down from the heavens.

219
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,560
Once word
of the poetry gathering spreads,

220
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,480
his name will resound throughout Daqian.

221
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,560
From there,
he'll rise straight to the top.

222
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:46,640
But the Zhou family,

223
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:50,080
having lost the imperial tribute status,

224
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,520
will have no way left

225
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,880
to stand against

226
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:54,720
the Marquis House.

227
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,520
He and I

228
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,680
are fated to walk
in two different worlds.

229
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,360
Parting sooner

230
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,040
is better for both of us.

231
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:17,140
(Xianquan Tavern)

232
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,640
Hey, Li Yunhe,

233
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,880
what's going on with you?

234
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,360
Have you stopped
making your milk pudding?

235
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,720
People outside keep asking about it.

236
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,080
I'm not in the mood.

237
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,920
Not even in the mood to make money?

238
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,680
Did one measly Xianquan Tavern

239
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,960
already wear you out?

240
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,720
This isn't like you at all.

241
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:41,720
I was kicked out of the Zhou family.

242
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,720
You've been discarded
by the Zhous for a long time,

243
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,880
but haven't you been staying there

244
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,160
all this time just fine?

245
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,680
They kicked you out all of a sudden.

246
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,840
What's their game?

247
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,120
I miss Yu.

248
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,280
Yu?

249
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:53,680
You mean that servant girl

250
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:55,240
from the Zhou Manor

251
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,720
who was always sticking around you?

252
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,840
Don't tell me

253
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,840
you wanted to buy out

254
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,320
the contract of that servant,

255
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,760
and that's why they threw you out?

256
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,240
I...

257
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:07,000
Anyway,
I can't explain it all to you clearly

258
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,360
in a few words.

259
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,440
If the Zhous won't release her,

260
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,360
this matter won't be easy to resolve.

261
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:14,240
The Zhou household
may not be what it once was,

262
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:16,280
but a lion in winter is still a lion.

263
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:18,120
Even if you keep
selling milk pudding day after day,

264
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,520
how long would you have to do that

265
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,880
before you could buy back

266
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:21,800
that servant girl?

267
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:23,560
You're right.

268
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,240
Even if I sell milk pudding
my whole life,

269
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,080
I could never match the Zhous' wealth.

270
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:31,960
This won't do.

271
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,640
I need to pull myself together.

272
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,360
I must get my fire back.

273
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,840
I gotta make money.

274
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,320
I have to be worthy of Yu.

275
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:40,720
Make money?

276
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:42,680
How do you plan to do that?

277
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:46,240
Haven't you noticed that Feng City

278
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,880
has been flooded with people recently?

279
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:50,840
We need to seize this chance

280
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,840
and make a killing.

281
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,000
Alright.

282
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:55,760
I've got your back.

283
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:14,960
Li Yunhe,

284
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,800
this "killing" you mentioned

285
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:18,600
means coming to the kitchen to gut fish?

286
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:20,240
I know you're a master of strategy,

287
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,320
cunning beyond compare,

288
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:22,920
but when it comes to cooking,

289
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,520
do you really know what you're doing?

290
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:26,120
What do you two know?

291
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,000
Just sit back
and watch me work my magic.

292
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:35,680
Yunzhuo,

293
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,400
tell me,

294
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:37,680
where on earth

295
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:38,600
did the Zhous

296
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,680
spot this guy

297
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:40,600
exactly?

298
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:43,000
He can compose poetry, match verses,

299
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,600
understands statecraft,

300
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:46,480
and he can practice medicine
and save lives.

301
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:47,840
And now he can pull

302
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,080
all these flashy skills out of his hat.

303
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:51,120
If I knew the answer to that,

304
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,800
it wouldn't have been
the Zhous' turn to spot him.

305
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,320
Yunzhuo, you've seen a lot of the world.

306
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,640
Have you ever seen dishes like these?

307
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,720
Never. I haven't even heard of them.

308
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,640
Here we go.

309
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,880
Alright now.

310
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:20,000
All the dishes are here.

311
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,200
Dig in.

312
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,400
These dishes of yours...

313
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,680
What are they called?

314
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:24,720
Never seen them before, huh?

315
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,320
Never tasted them, right?

316
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:26,840
Come on,

317
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,240
try it. See if it's good.

318
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,040
Hold it.

319
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:30,880
This stuff of yours?

320
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:32,280
One look and I can tell it's not good.

321
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,520
I'm not eating it.

322
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:34,320
You there.

323
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:34,600
I...

324
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,600
You try it first.

325
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,240
Come on then.

326
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,040
You go first.

327
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:45,800
No, wait!

328
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:46,600
Wait a second!

329
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:48,400
You can't eat that.

330
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,400
Wait.

331
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:53,960
Why stare at me like that?

332
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,240
What are you planning?

333
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:57,000
Shouldn't I be the one asking you that?

334
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,120
What are you planning?

335
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,880
Never mind.

336
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,440
Let me show you how it's done.

337
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:05,320
I'll have you know

338
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,200
that the finest ingredients

339
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:08,280
often require only

340
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:10,080
the simplest cooking methods.

341
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:14,800
Hot pot with plain water.

342
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,680
Dip it in slowly.

343
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,560
Savor it slowly.

344
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,080
And then

345
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:24,440
paired with my secret

346
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:26,320
scallion, ginger, and soy sauce dip.

347
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,600
Here. Taste it.

348
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,240
Well?

349
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:54,600
It's genuinely delicious!

350
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,640
Absolutely incredible!

351
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,720
Want to try some?

352
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,000
Heh.

353
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,760
All that mystic fuss,

354
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,880
and after all that,

355
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,800
it's just plain poached fish?

356
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:07,840
Exactly.

357
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,640
It's just poached fish.

358
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,480
What's the big deal?

359
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:11,760
Fine.

360
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:13,120
If you say it's poached fish,

361
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,120
then poached fish it is.

362
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,120
How about trying these then?

363
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:16,920
Steamed chicken.

364
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,720
Boneless crucian carp.

365
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,080
Dry-steamed spare ribs.

366
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:21,400
Lychee wood roast goose.

367
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,880
I can grasp
all the dishes you mentioned.

368
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,600
But this fish...

369
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,920
How did you make it boneless?

370
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,480
How to make it boneless?

371
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:31,080
With my superb

372
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,600
knife skills, of course.

373
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:36,000
(Fortunately, I used to be a foodie)

374
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,840
(and learned quite a few dishes)

375
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,080
(from state banquet chefs.)

376
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:40,640
(After transmigrating,)

377
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,880
(I've got one more survival skill
under my belt.)

378
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,400
Oh, enough with all this talk.

379
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:46,200
Do you want to try it or not?

380
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:46,920
Come on.

381
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:02,120
Delicious. Truly delicious!

382
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,680
So good!

383
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,440
I'll give it a try too.

384
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:34,120
Well?

385
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:44,440
Absolutely divine!

386
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,440
Miss Zhao,

387
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:47,080
we're at a tavern.

388
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:47,720
Could you maybe not make

389
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,200
those kinds of sounds while eating?

390
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:50,040
It's all too easy

391
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:51,240
for others to get the wrong idea.

392
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,680
Oh, mind your own business!

393
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:53,840
It's just really good.

394
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,200
Eat up then.

395
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:00,920
(Feng City is holding a grand
dragon boat festival.)

396
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,400
(Merchants and tycoons
from all over are gathering.)

397
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:05,680
(So I've got to seize this opportunity)

398
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:07,400
(to roll out more new signature dishes)

399
00:16:07,920 --> 00:16:09,000
(and take the reputation
of Xianquan Tavern)

400
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,040
(to the next level.)

401
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:12,000
Hey, let me be clear upfront.

402
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:14,520
This meal isn't on the house.

403
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:16,200
You'll have to work for it afterwards.

404
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,920
Sure, fine.

405
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:20,000
Whatever you need, just say the word

406
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,200
to my brother.

407
00:16:53,460 --> 00:16:57,060
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

408
00:16:57,220 --> 00:17:00,420
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

409
00:17:00,940 --> 00:17:03,660
♪Who took the March rain♪

410
00:17:03,900 --> 00:17:07,260
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

411
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:10,420
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

412
00:17:10,580 --> 00:17:13,780
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

413
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:20,580
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

414
00:17:20,620 --> 00:17:24,060
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

415
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:27,140
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

416
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:29,580
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

417
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:33,780
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

418
00:17:33,860 --> 00:17:37,140
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

419
00:17:37,300 --> 00:17:40,420
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

420
00:17:40,940 --> 00:17:43,860
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

421
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:50,540
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

422
00:18:16,820 --> 00:18:20,340
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

423
00:18:20,580 --> 00:18:23,740
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

424
00:18:24,340 --> 00:18:27,060
♪Who took the March rain♪

425
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:30,580
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

426
00:18:30,980 --> 00:18:33,860
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

427
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:37,660
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

428
00:18:37,700 --> 00:18:40,980
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

429
00:18:40,980 --> 00:18:43,940
♪As seasons change♪

430
00:18:43,940 --> 00:18:47,580
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

431
00:18:47,580 --> 00:18:50,420
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

432
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:53,060
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

433
00:18:53,060 --> 00:18:57,140
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

434
00:18:57,140 --> 00:19:00,460
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

435
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:04,180
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

436
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:07,700
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

437
00:19:07,700 --> 00:19:10,580
♪Only for you♪

438
00:19:10,580 --> 00:19:14,180
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

439
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:17,060
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

440
00:19:17,180 --> 00:19:19,740
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

441
00:19:19,740 --> 00:19:23,820
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

442
00:19:23,820 --> 00:19:27,140
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

443
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:30,540
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

444
00:19:31,380 --> 00:19:37,060
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

445
00:19:38,140 --> 00:19:42,260
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

446
00:19:43,540 --> 00:19:48,060
♪Your wedding gown♪
